      Parameters:
      paretoFront - the non-dominated solutions forming the Pareto front
      allPoints - all evaluated points (including dominated ones)
      objectiveNames - names of the objectives in order
      objectiveTypes - types (MAXIMIZE/MINIMIZE) for each objective
      totalIterations - total number of optimization iterations across all weights
